"],"url":"/product-page/isopropyl-alcohol-acs","documentImage":{"name":"b44a5c_abc6da576ab34945bba9ce49a8763529~mv2.png","height":1386.0,"width":1386.0},"description":"Solvent for Industrial Applications: Due to its ability to dissolve a wide range of non-polar compounds, 99% isopropyl alcohol is extensively used as a solvent in industries such as pharmaceuticals, cosmetics, and electronics. It's particularly useful for cleaning electronic components (such as circuit boards) because it evaporates quickly, leaving no residue. Cleaning Agent: In addition to its use as a solvent, 99% isopropyl alcohol is a powerful cleaning agent for removing sticky residues, ink stains, or grease from various surfaces.
